Package game.bonusGame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FillBucketAction
    This class represents the Action that fills the empty bucket
    RedeemAction
    Provides methods for its subclasses to redeem items.
    RedeemFertiliserAction
    This class represents the Action of redeeming the fertiliser for the stone tree
    RedeemSwordAction
    This class represents the Action of redeeming a sword
    RedeemTicketAction
    This class represents the Action of redeeming a ticket for intra-world teleportation
    StoneTree
    This class represents Stone Tree which is an Actor that drops stones and allows the player to redeem items
    TeleportAction
    This class represents an Action that teleports the actor
    TeleportationPad
    This class represents a TeleportationPad Item that allows actor to teleport
    TreeTalkAction  
    WaterTreeAction
    This class represents the Action that waters the stone tree
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BonusGameSkills
    A public enum that represents skills that a bonus game Item may possess BUCKETISFULL - indicates that the water bucket is filled with water BUCKETISEMPTY - indicates that the water bucket is empty TICKET - intra-world teleportation ticket FERTILISER -fertiliser for stone tree SWORD - sword, a WeaponItem redeemed from stone tree RIFLE - rifle, a WeaponItem redeemed from stone tree
